    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This car is looking for a dedicated new owner ready to bring it back to its former glory. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for a restoration project or a valuable source of parts at a very budget-friendly price!",
      "price": 4800.0,
